@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@repeatableCompletedProjectName = reopen_project_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatableNotCompletedProjectName = reopen_not_completed_project_case_{{$timestamp}}
@repeatableEmployeeCompletedProjectName = reopen_employee_personal_project_case_{{$timestamp}}
@missingProjectId = 999999
@invalidProjectId = 0

### 提示：正常路径和部分异常路径会先创建临时项目，因此可以重复回放

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：管理员创建待撤销完成的临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableCompletedProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证撤销项目完成接口。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2099-12-31"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableReopenProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员先完成刚创建的临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableReopenProjectId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：管理员撤销刚完成的临时项目，当前实现预期 status=2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableReopenProjectId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：管理员创建一个未完成的临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableNotCompletedProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证未完成项目不能撤销完成。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2099-12-31"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableNotCompletedProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录撤销项目完成，预期 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableReopenProjectId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：普通员工创建个人自用临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{repeatableEmployeeCompletedProjectName}}",
  "description": "用于验证管理员不能代撤销普通员工个人项目。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-01",
  "planned_end_date": "2099-12-31"
}

> {% client.global.set("repeatableEmployeeReopenProjectId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 正常路径：普通员工先完成自己的临时项目
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableEmployeeReopenProjectId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：管理员不能撤销普通员工创建的个人自用项目完成状态，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableEmployeeReopenProjectId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工撤销非本人负责项目完成状态，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableReopenProjectId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：当前不是已完成状态，不能撤销完成，预期 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableNotCompletedProjectId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableReopenProjectId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

[]

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}/reopen
Content-Type: application/json

{}
